
线程锁的种类
1） 互斥锁 mutex

线程锁的api
1）lock unlock
2) lock_guard
3) unique_lock
      unique_lock<std::mutex> l(myMutex_,try_to_lock)
      unique_lock<std::mutex> l(myMutex_,std::defer_lock)
                     1)可以随时使用lock unlock
                     2)release 还有返回他所管理的锁，进行解锁
                     3)转移所有权
      unique_lock<std::mutex> l(myMutex_,try_to_lock)
